{"tid":1565073,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"入到大學開始變得Anti social","createTime":"2019-09-13T04:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T06:46:03.000Z","uid":303168,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"342d9ba17a06d5375adda2780781f5be70ea75be","tid":1565073,"uid":303168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"由放榜到依家到差唔多一個月啦，<br />\n<br />\n兩個ocamp再加上堂同hall，識左接近80人咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（hi-bye friend)<br />\n相處上黎果陣絕對傾得到計，<br />\n唔會話無計傾唔會話會dead air。<br />\n不過每次拎到contact之後都係傾幾句就收線<br />\n唔會真係識到一個feel到會長期熟/真心既朋友<br />\n<br />\n無錯ocamp班人係玩得埋，願意每次叫你去食<br />\n飯一齊上堂一齊reg同一科<br />\n<br />\n但開始感到要刻意去扮玩得埋，為左令自己「唔會俾人覺得自己係孤單，唔會俾人覺得自己係被人<br />\n邊緣的一個」，呢種態度令自己好辛苦好難頂。<br />\n<br />\n然後開始唔去任何reu，唔會去天地堂間既食飯，<br />\n唔睇group message ，唔覆大同既任何邀請，<br />\n甚至想只依賴女朋友既陪伴去補償自己的空虛。<br />\n同埋間唔中搵翻一直以來既朋友。<br />\n<br />\n入左爛grade都搵到食既一科，而我竟然因為<br />\n無聊而去開始去讀書，真係一大諷刺<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87225b4a3d0f13a2f8d46b2c37b25b8e430086df","tid":1565073,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:08:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"5facbca2bbb38087784b17f22545ea53be00983e","ti